data.description: RANGELEY VILLAGE - ''The Peoples Choice'' rental property is for sale featuring a totally renovated 4 bed, 2 bath home with wonderful features and being sold absolutely turn key!  All fixtures, furnishings and furniture are being sold with this house, even the lawn mower in garage.  Active rental with built in clientele.  Wonderful location with a peak at Rangeley Cove and wonderful back yard.  Large sitting area with recently built fire-pit area.  Great quiet road that is close to all towns amenities that include restaurants, town beach and boat launch and RLRS school system. Great location to enjoy all 4 seasons, you can access ITS trails from the property on the access route.  Call today, this is a good one!
